          descriptionCondition0:
              "Welcome to Mayura. Mayura provides website features and other products and services to you when you visit or shop at &lt;mayura.com.kh&gt;, use Mayura products or services, use Mayura applications for mobile, or use software provided by Mayura in connection with any of the foregoing (collectively, \"Mayura Services\"). Mayura provides the Mayura Services subject to the following conditions.\n\nBy using Mayura Services, you agree to these conditions.Please read them carefully. \n\nWe offer a wide range of Mayura Services, and sometimes additional terms may apply. When you use an Mayura Service, you also will be subject to the guidelines, terms, and agreements applicable to that Mayura Service (\"Service Terms\"). If these Conditions of Use are inconsistent with the Service Terms, those Service Terms will control. \n\nBy accessing and/or using the Mayura Services, you agree to be bound by these Conditions of Use. If you do not agree to these Conditions of Use, do not access and/or use the Mayura Services.",
          descriptionCondition1: "Please review our Privacy Policy, which also governs your use of Mayura Services, to understand our practices.",
          descriptionCondition2:
