          descriptionCondition7:
              "You may need your own Mayura account to use certainMayura Services, and you may be required to be logged in to the account and have a valid payment method associated with it. If there is a problem charging your selected payment method, we may charge any other valid payment method associated with your account.You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and password and for restricting access to your account, and you agree to accept responsibility for all activities that occur under your account or password. Mayura does sell products for children, but it sells them to adults, who can purchase with a credit card or other permitted payment method. If you are under 18, you may use the Mayura Services only with involvement of a parent or guardian.Alcohol listings on Mayura are intended for adults. You must be at least 21 years of age to purchase alcohol, or use any site functionality related to alcohol. Mayura reserves the right to refuse service, terminate accounts, terminate your rights to use Mayura Services, remove or edit content, or cancel orders in its sole discretion.",
          descriptionCondition8:
              "You may post reviews, comments, photos, videos, and other content; send e-cards and other communications; and submit suggestions, ideas, comments, questions, or other information, so long as the content is not illegal, obscene, threatening, defamatory, invasive of privacy, infringing of intellectual property rights (including publicity rights), or otherwise injurious to third parties or objectionable, and does not consist of or contain software viruses, political campaigning, commercial solicitation, chain letters, mass mailings, or any form of \"spam\" or unsolicited commercial electronic messages.You may not use a false e-mail address, impersonate any person or entity, or otherwise mislead as to the origin of a card or other content. Mayura reserves the right (but not the obligation) to remove or edit such content, but does not regularly review posted content.\n\nIf you do post content or submit material, and unless we indicate otherwise, you grant Mayura nonexclusive, royalty-free, perpetual, irrevocable, and fully sublicensable right to use, reproduce, modify, adapt, publish, perform, translate, create derivative works from, distribute, and display such content throughout the world in any media.You grant Mayura and sublicensees the right to use the name that you submit in connection with such content, if they choose. You represent and warrant that you own or otherwise control all of the rights to the content that you post; that the content is accurate; that use of the content you supply does not violate this policy and will not cause injury to any person or entity; and that you will indemnify Mayura for all claims resulting from content you supply. Mayura has the right but not the obligation to monitor and edit or remove any activity or content. Mayura takes no responsibility and assumes no liability for any content posted by you or any third party.",
          descriptionCondition9:
              "Mayura respects the intellectual property of others. If you believe that your intellectual property rights are being infringed, please contact our Customer Service Team at &lt;087/092/068 762 762&gt; or &lt;info@mayura.com.kh&gt;.",
          descriptionCondition10:
              "Mayura attempts to be as accurate as possible. However, Mayura does not warrant that product descriptions or other content of any Mayura Service is accurate, complete, reliable,current, or error-free. If a product offered by Mayura itself is not as described, your sole remedy is to return it in unused condition.",
          descriptionCondition11:
              "\"List Price\" means the suggested retail price of a product as provided by a manufacturer, supplier, or seller. We regularly check List Prices against prices recently found on Mayura and other retailers. Certain products may have a \"Was Price\" displayed, which is determined using recent price history of the product on Mayura.\n\nWith respect to items sold by Mayura, we cannot confirm the price of an item until you order. Despite our best efforts, a small number of the items in our catalog may be mispriced. If the correct price of an item sold by Mayura is higher than our stated price, we will, at our discretion, either contact you for instructions before shipping or cancel your order and notify you of such cancellation. Other merchants may follow different policies in the event of a mispriced item.\n\nWe generally do not charge your credit card until after your order has entered the shipping process or, for digital products, until we make the digital product available to you.",
          descriptionCondition12:
              "When you use apps created by Mayura, such as the Mayura App, you may grant certain permissions to us for your device. Most mobile devices provide you with information about these permissions.",
          descriptionCondition13:
              "When you use Mayura Services, you agree not to: (a) impersonate any person or entity or to falsely state or otherwise misrepresent your affiliation with any person or entity; (b) use Mayura Services for illegal purposes; (c) attempt to gain unauthorized access to or otherwise interfere or disrupt other computer systems or networks connected to the Mayura Services;(d) post, promote, or transmit through Mayura Servies any prohibited materials; (e) interfere with another’s utilization of Mayura Services; (f) use or upload, in any way, any software or material that contains, or which you have reason to suspect that contains viruses, damaging components, malicious code, or harmful components which may impair or corrupt Mayura’s data or damage or interfere with the operation of another Customer’s computer or mobile device or the Mayura Services; and (g) use the Mayura Services other than in conformance with the acceptable use policies of any connected computer networks, any applicable internet standards, and any other applicable laws.",
          descriptionCondition14:
              "We may, from time to time and without giving any reason or prior notice, upgrade, modify, suspend or discontinue the provision of or remove, whether in whole or in part, the MayuraServices and shall not be liable if any such upgrade, modification, suspension or removal prevents you from accessing any part of the Mayura Services.",
          descriptionCondition15:
              "Parties other than Mayura operate stores, provide services or software, or sell product lines through Mayura Services. In addition, we provide links to the sites of affiliated companies and certain other businesses. If you purchase any of the products or services offered by these businesses or individuals, you are purchasing directly from those third parties, not from Mayura. We are not responsible for examining or evaluating, and we do not warrant, the offerings of any of these businesses or individuals (including the content of their websites). Mayura does not assume any responsibility or liability for the actions, product, and content of all these and any other third parties. You should carefully review their privacy statements and other conditions of use.",
          descriptionCondition16:
              "THE MAYURA SERVICES AND ALL INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING SOFTWARE) AND OTHER SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THE MAYURA SERVICES ARE PROVIDED BY MAYURA ON AN \"AS IS\" AND \"AS AVAILABLE\" BASIS, UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN WRITING. MAYURA MAKES NO REPRESENTATIONS OR WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, AS TO THE OPERATION OF THE MAYURA SERVICES, OR THE INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING SOFTWARE), OR OTHER SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THE MAYURA SERVICES UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN WRITING. YOU EXPRESSLY AGREE THAT YOUR USE OF THE MAYURA SERVICES IS AT YOUR SOLE RISK.\n\nTO THE FULL EXTENT PERMISSIBLE BY LAW, MAYURA DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO, IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY AND FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE. MAYURA DOES NOT WARRANT THAT THE MAYURA SERVICES, INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING SOFTWARE), OR OTHER SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THE MAYURA SERVICES, MAYURA\'S SERVERS, OR ELECTRONIC COMMUNICATIONS SENT FROM MAYURA ARE FREE OF VIRUSES OR OTHER HARMFUL COMPONENTS. TO THE FULL EXTENT PERMISSIBLE BY LAW, MAYURA WILL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES OF ANY KIND ARISING FROM THE USE OF ANY MAYURA SERVICE, OR FROM ANY INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING SOFTWARE), OR OTHER SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH ANY MAYURA SERVICE, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO DIRECT, INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, PUNITIVE, AND CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES, UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN WRITING.",
          descriptionCondition17:
              "Any dispute or claim relating in any way to your use of any Mayura Service or to any products or services sold or distributed by Mayura or through &lt;mayura.com.kh&gt; will be resolved by binding arbitration, rather than in court, except that you may assert claims in small claims court if your claims qualify. The arbitration law applies to this agreement.\n\nWe each agree that any dispute resolution proceedings will be conducted only on an individual basis and not in a class, consolidated, or representative action. If, for any reason, a claim proceeds in court rather than in arbitration we each waive any right to a jury trial. We also both agree that you or we may bring suit in court to enjoin infringement or other misuse of intellectual property rights.",
          descriptionCondition18:
              "By using any Mayura Service, you agree that the applicable laws of the Kingdom of Cambodia, without regard to principles of conflict of laws, will govern these Conditions of Use and any dispute of any sort that might arise between you and Mayura.",
          descriptionCondition19:
              "Please review our other policies. These policies also govern your use of Mayura Services. We reserve the right to make changes to our site, policies, Service Terms, and these Conditions of Use at any time. If any of these conditions shall be deemed invalid, void, or for any reason unenforceable, that condition shall be deemed severable and shall not affect the validity and enforceability of any remaining condition.",
          descriptionCondition20:
              "Subject to any Additional Agreements, the Conditions of Use constitute the entire agreement between you and Mayura with respect to and govern your use of the Mayura Services, superseding any prior written or oral agreements in relation to the same subject matter herein. You and Mayura are independent contractors, and no agency, partnership, joint venture, employee-employer, or franchiser-franchisee relationship is intended or created by the Conditions of Use. If you have any questions or comments on the Mayura Services, you may contact our Customer Service Team at &lt;087/092/068 762 762&gt; or &lt;info@mayura.com.kh&gt;.",

          titleShipping1: "1. Shipping Options",
          titleShipping2: "2. Order Tracking",
          titleShipping3: "3. Delivery",
          descriptionShipping1:
              "The following shipping options are available for Fulfilled by Seller (FBS) products purchased on Mayura:\n\n\n a. <b>Economy</b>:  If you are willing to 1-2 days for your items to be delivered, Mayura offers the Economy shipping method for all FBS products at free of charge.\n b. <b>Standard</b>: If you need your items to be delivered within a day, Mayura offers the Standard shipping method for FBS products at a flat rate of 1 USD.\n\nThe following shipping options are available for Fulfilled by Mayura (FBM) products purchased on Mayura:\n\t\t\ta. <b>Standard</b>: If you are willing to wait a day for your items to be delivered, Mayura offers the Standard shipping method for all FBM products at free of charge.\n\t\t\tb. <b>Express</b>: If you need your items to be delivered within 3 hours, Mayura offers the Express shipping method exclusively for FBM products at a flat rate of 1 USD.\n\nYou will be able to assess all the available shipping options and their respective rates on the checkout page before you place your order.",
          descriptionShipping2:
              "For all orders placed using one of the three shipping options (Economy, Standard, Express) provided by Mayura , a tracking number will be issued by the courier service provider, which should appear on your “My Orders” page.\n\nYou can track your order at any time by following these steps:\n\nYou can track your order at any time by following these steps:\n\t\t\ta. Log into your Mayura Account\n\t\t\tb. Go to “My Orders” on your “Account” page\n\t\t\tc. Select the order you would like to track\n\t\t\td. Click on “Track Package” to track the status of your shipment",
          descriptionShipping3:
              "Operating hours may differ depending on the courier service provider. However, for standard delivery service, you can expect your item to be delivered from 8:00am to 8:00 pm both on weekdays and weekends.\n\nFor an exact date and time of delivery, our courier service providers will contact you prior to attempting delivery. If you are not available at the time of delivery, your shipment will be returned and the courier service provider will try to contact you again the next working day.\n\nPlease note that the order will be automatically canceled in the case that our courier service provider cannot contact you, so it is very important that you provide us with correct andup-to-date contact information.",

          titleReturn1: "1.Mayura Return Policy",
          titleReturn2: "Software",
          titleReturn3: "Electronics",
          titleReturn4: "2.Seller Return Policy",
          titleReturn5: "3.Return Conditions",
          titleReturn6: "4.Refund Policy",
          titleReturn7: "5.Cancellation Policy",
          descriptionReturn1:
              "Items purchased on Mayura can be returned within seven (7) days of receipt of shipment in most cases. Some products have different policies or requirements associated with them.\n\nUnder the Mayura Return Policy, the following conditions apply to Change of Mind returns:\n• All item packaging, documentation (boxes, manuals, warranty cards, etc.) and certificates of authenticity, grading, and appraisal must be returned with thereturned items. Packaging must be unopened and seals intact (where applicable).\n• Items must be in new and unworn condition.\n• Any items that, because of customer negligence, misuse, or tampering are damaged, missing parts, or in unsellable condition, will not be accepted for return.\n• Any item(s) that have been resized, damaged, or otherwise altered after delivery will not be accepted for return.\nThese conditions apply only to change of mind returns and do not apply to items that are returned because they are damaged or faulty.",
          descriptionReturn2:
              "Software is a unique category and has specific guidelines.\n• If the product was sold in new condition and has been opened, it cannot be returned unless it is defective.\n• If the product is materially different, it can be returned in its original condition, as long as it is postmarked within seven (7) days of the delivery of the original shipment.",
          descriptionReturn3:
              "Buyers can return electronics if the products are postmarked within seven (7) days of the delivery of the original shipment.\n• If the item is defective or damaged upon receipt, the buyer must report the defect or damage to you within two (2) days of receipt and arrange a return.\n• If the item becomes defective more than seven (7) days after shipment and is under warranty, Mayura or the third-party seller will assist you in pursuinga warranty claim with the manufacturer.\n\n<b>Note</b>: Before you return a product that has non-volatile internal memory (like an MP3 player or a digital camera), make sure to clear the devices of any personal data. Non-volatile memory is any computerized memory that can keep information stored even when not powered.",
          descriptionReturn4:
              "When you order from a third-party seller that fulfills and ships its own inventory, your return is sent back to the seller instead of Mayura. While most sellers offer a returns policy equivalent to Mayura\’s, some seller returns policies may vary.\n\nThird-party sellers must either provide a return address within the Kingdom of Cambodia, provide return shipping without charge, or offer a full refund without requesting the item be returned. If a seller does not offer these methods to return your items, you may file a claim to seek help with your return.",
          descriptionReturn5:
              "In order for an item to be eligible for a return, one or more of the following conditions must be met:\na.  Damaged: Item that is damaged on arrival or has broken packaging. To return a damaged item, the plastic wrap or seal of the item must be intact and all packaging and accessories must be included.\nb.  Wrong Item: Item received is not what you ordered. To return a wrong item, the item must not have been used, is sealed, and in original condition, with all packaging and accessories included.\nc.  Defective Item: Item does not function as described by the seller. To return a defective item, though it can be tested, it must be in a “new” condition without any cosmetic damages and include all packaging and accessories.\nd.  Not as Advertised: Item is different from the description or the photo on the product page. to return a not as advertised item, the item must not have been used, is sealed, and in original condition with all packaging and accessories.\ne.  Change of Mind: Item is no longer needed or wanted. To return a change of mind item, the item must not have been used, must be sealed, and in original condition with all packaging and accessories.\nf.  Wrong Size: Item does not fit because it is too big/small. To return a wrong size item,though it can be tested, it must be in a “new”  codition without any cosmetic damages and  include all packaging and accessories.\n\n<b>Note: </b>Not all sellers on Mayura may accept returns for all conditions listed above.",
          descriptionReturn6:
              "Upon successful return of an item, Mayura and/or the third-party seller will assess whether the returned item would be eligible for a refund. If the returned item qualifies for a refund, a full refund will be issued to you in the method the payment was originally made to purchase the item. However, at the sole discretion of Mayura, you may, at certain situations, be given an option to select a method of refund. Please note that it may take up to fifteen (15) days to process a reversal of payment made by credit card.",
          descriptionReturn7:
              "You are eligible to cancel any order you have placed within thirty (30) minutes of order placement. Furthermore, you are eligible to cancel any order that is in “Pending” status. You will not be charged any fees for successful order cancellations. However, please note that an order may not be canceled once it is shipped by Mayura or the third-party seller.",

